title: O'Mamma Mia
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Pizza, Italian, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Pizza restaurant with several vegan pizzas on the menu. Pizza chef previously worked at Tevere in Soder. All vegan products courtesy of goodstore. Large menu of pizza, pasta and Mexican dishes. Aug 13, 2013 reported open.
